## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of sources and the inherent biases present in opinion pieces and philosophical arguments. The complexity of the issue means that perspectives can vary widely based on cultural, religious, and personal beliefs. Additionally, the legal status of euthanasia varies by jurisdiction, which can influence the arguments presented in different regions.

